Class AbstractJslipcMessage

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jslipc.ipc.pipe.AbstractJslipcMessage
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    JslipcRequest, JslipcResponse

    public abstract class AbstractJslipcMessage
extends Object
    Abstract base class for both JslipcRequest and JslipcResponse.
